      "score": 35,
      "comments": 19,
      "author": "confusedalex",
      "published": "2026-07-03T23:23:43Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Minimize homelab toil by adopting GitOps with Flux or ArgoCD and Terraform to automate patching, configuration, and self-healing.",
        "Replace complex VPNs and ingress setups with zero-trust overlays like Tailscale or Cloudflare Tunnels to reduce manual network maintenance.",
        "Shift from heavy hypervisors to lightweight, low-maintenance container stacks like Docker Compose or K3s to minimize OS-level upkeep."
      ]
    },
